high_descs: Go to the counter to the left of the toaster.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter.
Turn to the counter on the left of the sink.
Slice the lettuce on the counter.
Move away from the counter.
Set the butter knife in front of the lettuce on the counter.
Move back to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Move over to the sink on the right.
Wash the lettuce in the sink.
Take the cleaned lettuce to the counter to the left of the sink.
Set the lettuce down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed piece of lettuce on the counter by the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, go towards the sink, turn left and go to the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right and go to the lettuce beside the sink.
Cut the lettuce on the counter.
Turn left and then turn back around.
Put the knife on the counter in front of the lettuce.
Turn left towards the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink, rinse it and pick it back up.
Turn left and then turn around.
Put the slice of lettuce on the counter by the salt.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean slice of lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: move forward facing the counter that is to the right of the stove
pick up the butter knife that is on the counter to the right of the stove
turn to the right and move slightly to the right to face the head of lettuce on the counter
cut the head of lettuce that is on the counter with the knife
turn to the right staying in place
put the knife on to the counter in front of the head of lettuce
turn to the left to face the counter with the head of lettuce
pick up the end slice of the lettuce from the counter
move to the right to face the sink
put the lettuce slice in to the sink, turn on the faucet to rinse off the slice, turn off the water and pick up the lettuce slice from the sink
move to the left to face the counter to the left of the sink and to the left of the remaining head of lettuce and turn to the right
put the slice of lettuce on to the counter to the right of the sink next to the salt shaker
anns.task_desc: put a clean slice of lettuce on to the counter
